hadiths[30]{hadithnumber,text}:
5545,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj (eidul-Az'haa ke din) ki shuruaat ham Namaz (eid) se karengey phir wapas aa kar qurbani karengey jo is tarah karega wo hamari sunnat ke mutabiq karega lekin jo shakhs (namaaze-eid se) pahley zabah karega to uski haisiyat sirf gosht ki hogi jo usney apne ghar walon ke liye taiyaar kar liya hai qurbani wo hargiz bhi nahi. is par abu-Barda-bin-Niyaar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey unhon-ne (namaz eid se pahley hi ( zabah kar liya tha aur arz kya ke mere paas aik saal se kam Umr ka bakra hai (kya uski dobara qurbani ab Namaz ke baad kar loon?) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski qurbani kar lo lekin tumharey baad ye kisi aur ke liye kafi nahi hoga. Mutarrif ne Aamir se bayan kya aur unse Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Namaz eid ke baad qurbani ki uski qurbani poori hogi aur us ne musalmanon ki sunnat ke mutabiq amal kya.
5546,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Namaz eid se pahley qurbani kar li us ne apni zaat ke liye janwar zabah kya aur jisne Namaz eid ke baad qurbani ki uski qurbani poori hui. us ne musalmanon ki sunnat ko pa liya.
5547,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba mein qurbani ke janwar taqseem kiye. Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ke hisse mein aik saal se kam ka bakri ka bachcha aaya. unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere hisse main to aik saal se kam ka bachcha aaya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum usi ki qurbani kar lo.
5548,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) unke paas aaey wo Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil honey se pahley maqam sarf main haaiza ho gaee thin. us waqt aap ro rahi thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat hai kya tumhen haiz ka khoon aaney laga hai? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya ke ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to Allah Taala ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ki betiyon ke muqaddar mein likh diya hai. tum haajiyon ki tarah tamam aa'maale-Haj ada kar lo bas Baitullah ka tawaaf na karo, phir jab ham Mina mein they, to hamarey paas gaaey ka gosht laya gaya. maine puchha ke ye kya hai? logon ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se gaaey ki qurbani ki hai."
5549,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke din farmaya ke jisne Namaz eid se pahley qurbani zabah kar li hai wo dobara qurbani karey is par aik sahib ne khadey ho kar arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye wo din hai jis mein gosht khaney ki khahish hoti hai phir unhon-ne apne padausiyon ka zikr kya aur (kaha ke) mere paas aik saal se kam ka bakri ka bachcha hai jiska gosht 2 bakriyon ke gosht se behtar hai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein uski ijazat de di. mujhey nahi malum ke ye ijazat dusron ko bhi hai ya nahi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 mendhon ki taraf mudey aur unhein zabah kya phir log bakriyon ki taraf badhey aur unhein taqseem karke (zabah kya).
5550,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zamana phir kar usi haalat par aa gaya hai jis haalat par us din tha jis din Allah Taala ne aasman w zameen paida kiye they. saal baara mahina ka hota hai unmein char hurmat ke mahiney hain, teen pai-dar-pai zii-Qa'da, Zil-Hijja aur Mohrim aur aik muzar ka rajab jo jumaadal-Ukhraa aur Shoban ke darmyan mein padta hai. (phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya) ye kon sa mahina hai, ham ne arz kya Allah aur uske rasool zyada jantey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. ham ne samjha ke shayad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska koi aur naam rakhengey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya ye Zil-Hijja nahi hai? ham ne arz kya Zil-Hijja hi hai. phir farmaya ye kon sa Shahar hai? ham ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool ko iska zyada ilm hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey aur ham ne samjha ke shayad aap iska koi aur naam rakhengey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya ye Makka Mukarrama nahi hai? ham ne arz kya kyon nahi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ye din kon sa hai? ham ne arz kya ke Allah aur uske rasool ko iska behtar ilm hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey aur ham ne samjha ke aap iska koi aur naam tajwiz karengey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya ye qurbani ka din nahi hai? ham ne arz kya kyon nahi ! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya to tumhara khoon , tumharey maal, Muhammad-bin-Siiriin ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke (ibne-Ubaii bakra ne) ye bhi kaha ke aur tumhari izzat tum par (eik ki doosrey par) is tarah baa-hurmat hain jis tarah us din ki hurmat tumharey is Shahar main aur is maheene mein hai aur an-qareeb apne rab se milogey us waqt wo tum se tumharey aamaal ke barey mein sawal karega. aagah ho jao mere baad gumrah na ho jana ke tum mein se kuchh kuchh doosrey ki gardan maarney lagey. haan jo yahan maujood hain wo (meraa ye paighaam) ghair maujood logon ko pahuncha dein. mumkin hai ke kuchh wo jinhein ye paigham pahunchaya jaey kuchh unse zyada usey mehfooz karne waley hon jo isey sun rahe hain. is par Muhammad-bin-Siiriin kaha kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sach farmaya, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aagah ho jao kya maine (iska paigham tum ko) pahuncha diya hai. aagah ho jao kya maine pahuncha diya hai?"
5551,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) qurbaan gaah mein nehar kya kartey they aur Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke murad wo jagah hai jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qurbani kartey they.
5552,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( qurbani ( zabah aur nehar eidgaah mein kya kartey they.
5553,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 mendhon ki qurbani kartey they aur main bhi 2 mendhon ki qurbani karta tha.
5554,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) seeng waley 2 chitkabrey mendhon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur unhein apne hath se zabah kya. uski mutabiat (pairavi) Wuhaib ne ki, unse Ayub ne aur Ismail aur Haakim-bin-Wardaan ne bayan kya ke unse Ayub ne, unse Muhammad-bin-Siiriin ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya."
5555,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba mein taqseem karne ke liye aapko kuchh qurbani ki bakriyan diin unhon-ne unhein taqseem kya phir aik saal se kam ka aik bachcha bach gaya to unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska tazkira kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski qurbani tum kar lo.
5556,"mere maamun abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) ne eid ki Namaz se pahley hi qurbani kar li thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tumhari bakri sirf gosht ki bakri hai. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere paas aik saal se kam Umr ka aik bakri ka bachcha hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum usey hi zabah kar lo lekin tumharey baad) uski qurbani ( kisi aur ke liye jaaiz nahi hogi phir farmaya jo shakhs Namaz eid se pahley qurbani kar leta hai wo sirf apne khaney ko janwar zabah karta hai aur jo eid ki Namaz ke baad qurbani karey uski qurbani poori hoti hai aur wo musalmanon ki sunnat ko pa leta hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ubeda ne Shabi aur Ibrahim ne ki aur uski mutabiat (pairavi) Wakee ne ki, unse Hurais ne aur unse Shabi ne ( bayan kya (aur Aasim aur Dawud ne Shabi se bayan kya ke '' mere paas aik doodh peeti pathiya hai.'' aur Zubeda aur faraas ne Shabi se bayan kya ke '' mere paas aik saal se kam Umr ka bachcha hai.'' aur abul-Ahwas ne bayan kya, unse Mansoor ne bayan kya ke ''eik saal se kam ki pathiya . ''aur ibne-aun ne bayan kya ke ''eik saal se kam Umr ki doodh peeti pathiya hai.''"
5557,"abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) ne namaaze-eid se pahley qurbani zabah kar li thi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke iske badley mein dusri qurbani kar lo. unhon-ne arz kya ke mere paas aik saal se kam Umr ke bachchey ke siwa aur koi janwar nahi. Shoba ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi kaha tha ke wo aik saal ki bakri se bhi umda hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir usi ki iske badley mein qurbani kar do lekin tumharey baad ye kisi ke liye kafi nahi hogi aur Haatim-bin-Wardaan ne bayan kya, unse Ayub ne, unse Muhammad ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aakhir hadis tak (is riwayat mein ye lafz hain) ke ''eik saal se kam Umr ki bachchii hai.''"
5558,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 chitkabrey mendhon ki qurbani ki. maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne paon janwar ke uper rakhey huey hain aur bismillaahi-Allaahu-akbar padh rahe hain. is tarah aap ne donon mendhon ko apne hath se zabah kya.
5559,"maqam sarf main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur main ro rahi thi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya baat hai, kya tumhen haiz aa gaya hai? maine arz kya ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to Allah Taala ne Adam ki betiyon ki taqdeer mein likh diya hai. isliye haajiyon ki tarah tamam aa'maale Haj anjam do sirf Kaba ka tawaaf na karo aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne beeviyon ki taraf se gaaey ki qurbani ki."
5560,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they. khutbe mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj ke din ki shuruaat ham Namaz (eid) se karengey phir wapas aa kar qurbani karengey jo shakhs is tarah karega wo hamari sunnat ko pa lega lekin jisne (eid ki Namaz se pahley) janwar zabah kar liya to wo aisa gosht hai jisey usne apne ghar walon ke khaney ke liye taiyaar kya hai wo qurbani kisi darje mein bhi nahi. abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! maine to eid ki Namaz se pahley qurbani kar li hai albatta mere paas abhi aik saal se kam Umr ka aik bakri ka bachcha hai aur saal bhar ki bakri se behtar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum usi ki qurbani uske badle mein karo lekin tumharey baad ye kisi ke liye jaaiz na hoga."
5561,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Namaz se pahley qurbani kar li ho wo dobara qurbani kare. is par aik sahabi uthey aur arz kya : (ya rasoolullaah!) us din gosht ki logon ko khahish zyada hoti hai phir unhon-ne apne padausiyon ki mohtaajii ka zikr kya jaisey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka uzr qabool kar liya ho ( unhon-ne ye bhi kaha ke) mere paas aik saal ka aik bachcha hai aur bakriyon se bhi achchha hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein iske qurbani ki ijazat de di lekin mujhey iska ilm nahi ke ye ijazat dusron ko bhi thi ya nahi phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 mendhon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey. unki murad ye thi ke unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zabah kya phir log bakriyon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur unhein zabah kya.
5562,qurbani ke din main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Namaz se pahley qurbani kar li ho wo uski jagah dobara karey aur jisne qurbani abhi na ki ho wo kare.
5563,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din Namaz eid padhi aur farmaya ke jo hamari tarah Namaz padhta ho aur hamarey qible ko qibla banata ho wo namaaze-eid se farigh honey se pahley qurbani na kare. is par abu-Barda-bin-Niyaar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! maine to qurbani kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir wo aik aisi cheez hui jisey tum ne waqt se pahley hi kar liya hai. unhon-ne arz kya mere paas aik saal se kam Umr ka aik bachcha hai jo aik saal ki 2 bakriyon se umda hai. kya main usey zabah kar loon. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kar lo lekin tumharey baad ye kisi aur ke liye jaaiz nahi hai. Aamir ne bayan kya ke ye unki behtreen qurbani thi.
5564,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) seeng waley 2 chitkabrey mendhon ki qurbani kya kartey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna paon unki gardanon ke uper rakhtey aur unhein apne hath se zabah kartey they.
5565,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne seeng waley 2 chitkabrey mendhon ki qurbani ki. unhein apne hath se zabah kya. bismillaahi Allahu-akbar padha aur apna paon unki gardan ke uper rakh kar zabah kya.
5566,"wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein aaey aur arz kya ke ummul-momeneen! agar koi shakhs qurbani ka janwar Kaba mein bhej de aur khud apne Shahar mein muqeem ho aur jiske zariey bhejey usey uski wasiiyat kar de ke iske janwar ke galley main (nishaanii ke taur par) aik haar pehna diya jaey to kya us din se wo us waqt tak ke liye mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ho jaeyga jab tak haji apna ehram na khol lein. bayan kya ke is par maine pardey ke peechhey Ummul-Momenin ke apne aik hath se doosrey hath par maarney ki awaz suni aur unhon-ne kaha, main khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qurbani ke janwaron ke haar bandhti thi, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey Kaba bhejtey they lekin logon ke wapas honey tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par koi cheez haram nahi hoti thi jo unke ghar ke doosrey logon ke liye halal ho."
5567,Madina pahunchne tak ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein qurbani ka gosht jama kartey they aur kai martaba ( bajaey ( لحوم الأضاحي ( ke) ( لحوم الهدى‏ . Mina (ka lafz istemal kya.
5568,wo safar mein they jab wapas aaey to unke samney gosht laya gaya. kaha gaya ke ye hamari qurbani ka gosht hai. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke usey hataao mein usey nahi chakhoonga. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir uth gaya aur ghar se bahar nikal kar apne bhai abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya wo maa ki taraf se unke bhai they aur badr ki ladai mein shirkat karne walon mein se they. maine unse iska zikr kya aur unhon-ne kaha ke tumharey baad hukm badal gaya hai.
5569,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne tum mein se qurbani ki to teesrey din wo us haalat mein subah karey ke uske ghar mein qurbani ke gosht mein se kuchh bhi baqi na ho. doosrey saal sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! kya ham is saal bhi wahi karein jo pichhley saal kya tha. (ke teen din se zyada qurbani ka gosht bhi na rakhein). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab khaao, khilaao aur jama karo. pichhley saal to chunkey log tangi mein mubtala they, isliye maine chaha ke tum logon ki mushkilaat mein unki madad karo."
5570,Madina mein ham qurbani ke gosht mein namak laga kar rakh detey they aur phir usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhi pesh kartey they phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qurbani ka gosht teen din se zyada na khaya karo. ye hukm zaroori nahi tha balke aap ka mansha ye tha ke ham qurbani ka gosht (un logon ko bhi jinke yahan qurbani na hui ho ( khilaaein aur Allah zyada jaanney wala hai.
5571,mujhey ibne- azhar ke ghulam abu Ubaid ne bayan kya ke wo Baaqar eid ke din umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath eidgaah mein maujood they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutbe se pahley eid ki Namaz padhai phir logon ke samney khutba diya aur khutbe mein farmaya aey logo ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen 2 Eidon mein roza rakhney se mana farmaya hai aik wo din hai jis din tum ( Ramazan ke) rozey poorey karke iftaar kartey ho ( eidul-fitr (aur doosra tumhari qurbani ka din hai.
5572,"phir main Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath (unki khilafat ke zamane mein eidgaah mein) hazir tha. us din Juma bhi tha. aap ne khutbe se pahley Namaz eid padhai phir khutba diya aur farmaya ke aey logo ! aaj ke din tumharey liye 2 eidein jama ho gaee hain. ( eid aur Juma ( aas-paas ke rehney walon mein se jo shakhs pasand karey Juma ka bhi intizar karey aur agar koi wapas jana chahey (namaz eid ke baad hi ( to wo wapas ja sakta hai, maine usey ijazat de di hai."
5573,phir main eid ki Namaz mein Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath aaya. unhon-ne bhi Namaz khutbe se pahley padhai phir logon ko khutba diya aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen apni qurbani ka gosht teen din se zyada khaney ki manaahii ki hai aur Mamar ne Zohri se aur unse abu-Ubaida ne isi tarah bayan kya.
5574,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qurbani ka gosht teen din tak khaao. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Mina se kooch kartey waqt roti Zaitoon ke tel se khaatey, kyonke wo qurbani ke gosht se ( teen din ke baad) parhez kartey they."
